snippet.textDisplay:
"Ravi to chenab puchda ki haal ae satluj da."
Ravi marks the boundary btw indian punjab and pakistan punjab. chenab lies in pakistan while satluj flows in india.
This line signifies the respect and appreciation the people of each side have for other. But also emphasizes the division of 1947 which divided one punjab into two along the ravi river. The culture,language, food still remains the same yet  our social and cultural relations are very weak.
